Actions
Call
1. text contains a phone number
2. Text contains the word "call" followed by "the", "your", "our"
3. Text contains a script beginning with "i am calling"
Text
1.Text contains "send a message to"
2. Text contains the word countable
3. Text contains the word resistbot
Write
1. Text contains some combination of send, write, letter, and postcard
2. Text contains phrase "thank you note"
Petition
1. Text contains "sign" then 0 to five words and "petition"
2. Text contains the word "petition"
Twitter
1. Text contains a twitter handle preceded by the word tweet
2. Text contains a hashtag preceded by the word tweet
Donate
1. Text contains the word "donate"
2. Text contains the word "donations"
3. Text contains the word "donating"
4. Text contains "contribute" or "give" followed by some amount of money
Email
1. Text contains an email address 
2. Text contains "email" followed by "your" or "the 

Phone Bank
1. Text contains "phone bank"
Volunteer
1. Text contains "volunteer opportunities"